~My default userpic is Envy because for some obscene reason, I like the psychotic little palmtree head, in spite of all all the crap he pulls. XD;

Welp, went to a college fair today. O.o Man, felt <i>exactly</i> like the dealer's room at I-CON, I swear. 'Cept at I-CON you need to pay for the stuff...here they just kinda say "take it! =D". Wouldn't it be nice if they did that at I-CON? I sure as hell wouldn't mind. XD;

Seems as though they're starting an anime club in school. Hope so. Even if the guys who are planning on starting it don't actually start it, we're talking about doing it anyway since so many people are interested so far. Squee. Won't make me miss the old RAMEN days any less though. XD;

Oh yeah. I keep meaning to mention this. O.o Anyone remember the old Gargoyles animated series? Well, they're releasing the first season (13 episodes) onto DVD this December. Which will include a crapload of awesome extras from what I heard. X3 Plus, if the sales go well enough, they'll release more...and if those do well enough, they're going to take up production of the series again. Possibly even completely eliminating the Goliath Chronicles (which is good, since the director-person was only actually involved in the first episode of it o.o;). *bouncebounce* Never hurts to be hopeful, ne? XD *crosses fingers for that*
